# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:12
translate german jamie1_777c0e1d:

    # "I see Jamie leaving her house and walking out towards her car. I wave at her."
    "Ich sehe, wie Jamie ihr Haus verlässt und zu ihrem Auto geht. Ich winke ihr zu."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:15
translate german jamie1_2848acf3:

    # gnd "Hey there."
    gnd "Hey."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:17
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_008.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_008.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:18
translate german jamie1_d7b2148b:

    # gnd "I'm going out for a coffee before class. Want to join me?"
    gnd "Ich gehe vor dem Unterricht noch einen Kaffee trinken. Kommst du mit?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:19
translate german jamie1_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Klar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:20
translate german jamie1_d60e5294:

    # gnd "Do you know where Java Lava is?"
    gnd "Weißt du, wo Java Lava ist?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:21
translate german jamie1_6ff82333:

    # pc "Yep."
    pc "Ja."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:23
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_006.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_006.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:24
translate german jamie1_55e7809c:

    # gnd "Cool, meet me there."
    gnd "Cool, treffen wir uns dort."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:26
translate german jamie1_2d0bcd97:

    # "She smiles and gets into her car before pulling out and heading down the road."
    "Sie lächelt und steigt in ihr Auto, bevor sie losfährt und die Straße hinunterfährt."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:29
translate german jamie1_1da96612:

    # "I get into my car and quickly follow her."
    "Ich steige in mein Auto und fahre ihr schnell hinterher."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:30
translate german jamie1_50a2f2a6:

    # "I wonder why she didn't just want to ride together. It's a little weird since we're coming from pretty much the same place."
    "Ich frage mich, warum sie nicht einfach mitfahren wollte. Es ist ein bisschen seltsam, da wir ja fast vom selben Ort kommen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:32
translate german jamie1_f376757c:

    # "I pull into the Java Lava parking lot and can smell the scent of the coffee drifting out of the entire building."
    "Ich fahre auf den Parkplatz von Java Lava und kann den Duft des Kaffees riechen, der aus dem ganzen Gebäude strömt."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:33
translate german jamie1_01e0166e:

    # "I park next to Jamie, who is still sitting in her car."
    "Ich parke neben Jamie, die noch in ihrem Auto sitzt."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:34
translate german jamie1_15a1f80d:

    # "She steps out at the same time that I do."
    "Sie steigt zur gleichen Zeit aus wie ich."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:38
translate german jamie1_32e82c5b:

    # gnd "Hey there, fancy meeting you here."
    gnd "Hey, was für ein Zufall, dich hier zu treffen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:39
translate german jamie1_c2309d17:

    # pc "It is quite a coincidence. Shall we drink together?"
    pc "Das ist ja ein ziemlicher Zufall. Sollen wir zusammen etwas trinken?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:40
translate german jamie1_bb6e9df1:

    # gnd "Yes, I think we should."
    gnd "Ja, ich finde, das sollten wir."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:41
translate german jamie1_bec125c3:

    # "We walk up to the front door together. I hold the door open and the barista greets us as we walk in."
    "Wir gehen gemeinsam zur Eingangstür. Ich halte die Tür auf und die Barista begrüßt uns, als wir hereinkommen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:45
translate german jamie1_f6e4b44a:

    # "She looks familiar, but I can't place her. Probably just somebody I've seen around town. It's not a very big place."
    "Sie kommt mir bekannt vor, aber ich kann sie nicht zuordnen. Wahrscheinlich nur jemand, den ich schon mal in der Stadt gesehen habe. Es ist kein sehr großer Laden."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:47
translate german jamie1_f1d232e2:

    # "Tammy is working again today. I guess she works a lot."
    "Tammy arbeitet heute wieder. Ich schätze, sie arbeitet viel."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:48
translate german jamie1_e532df5e:

    # "Jamie and I place our orders, and the barista makes them without much small talk."
    "Jamie und ich geben unsere Bestellungen auf, und die Barista bereitet sie zu, ohne viel Smalltalk zu machen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:49
translate german jamie1_4b7ec1d8:

    # "Then we take our drinks and sit across from each other at a small table in the dining area."
    "Dann nehmen wir unsere Getränke und setzen uns einander gegenüber an einen kleinen Tisch im Gastraum."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:52
translate german jamie1_7ca9f991:

    # "Jamie seems unusually shy. We'd never had a problem talking to each other when we were younger, but things are different now."
    "Jamie wirkt ungewöhnlich schüchtern. Als wir jünger waren, hatten wir nie Probleme, miteinander zu reden, aber jetzt ist alles anders."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:53
translate german jamie1_e60beee6:

    # "She simply looks at me, and when I look back, she averts her eyes and smiles."
    "Sie sieht mich einfach nur an, und als ich zurückblicke, wendet sie den Blick ab und lächelt."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:54
translate german jamie1_4d348656:

    # "I don't know what to talk about really."
    "Ich weiß eigentlich nicht, worüber ich reden soll."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:55
translate german jamie1_3fd979ca:

    # pc "So, you're going to school this semester?"
    pc "Du gehst also dieses Semester zur Uni?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:56
translate german jamie1_cefd0447:

    # "It seems like an easy question to get us started talking about something."
    "Das scheint eine einfache Frage zu sein, um ins Gespräch zu kommen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:58
translate german jamie1_e7bf7de1:

    # gnd "Yeah, Skyhill."
    gnd "Ja, Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:59
translate german jamie1_076d61a1:

    # pc "What's your major?"
    pc "Was studierst du?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:60
translate german jamie1_a9ffb9a9:

    # gnd "I'm in the teaching program. I'll be starting my in-class assistant position this semester, where I help a teacher for two periods a day."
    gnd "Ich bin im Lehramtsstudium. Ich fange dieses Semester als Klassenassistentin an, wo ich einem Lehrer zwei Stunden am Tag helfe."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:61
translate german jamie1_53927809:

    # pc "Oh, that's exciting."
    pc "Oh, das ist spannend."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:62
translate german jamie1_d7ae6789:

    # gnd "Yeah, I'm pretty nervous about it actually."
    gnd "Ja, eigentlich bin ich ziemlich nervös deswegen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:63
translate german jamie1_5924379f:

    # pc "You shouldn't be. You'll do great, I'm sure."
    pc "Das solltest du nicht sein. Du wirst das toll machen, da bin ich mir sicher."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:64
translate german jamie1_30b2342d:

    # pc "It doesn't surprise me that you're going to become a teacher."
    pc "Es überrascht mich nicht, dass du Lehrerin werden willst."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:65
translate german jamie1_d096758b:

    # pc "You always used to help me with my schoolwork. I don't think I would have passed 8th grade English without your help."
    pc "Du hast mir immer bei meinen Hausaufgaben geholfen. Ich glaube nicht, dass ich ohne deine Hilfe den Englischkurs in der 8. Klasse bestanden hätte."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:67
translate german jamie1_8ab7f6ac:

    # gnd "Oh you definitely wouldn't have. Your essays were horrible."
    gnd "Oh, das hättest du definitiv nicht. Deine Aufsätze waren furchtbar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:68
translate german jamie1_ba5dd62d:

    # pc "They didn't get much better in high school either, or college."
    pc "In der Oberstufe oder an der Uni sind sie auch nicht viel besser geworden."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:70
translate german jamie1_4bc7c623:

    # gnd "So what are you majoring in?"
    gnd "Und was studierst du?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:71
translate german jamie1_8dfe1fc1:

    # pc "Quantum Science, but I'm having to take all my basics this year, since I didn't take them before."
    pc "Quantenwissenschaft, aber ich muss dieses Jahr alle Grundlagenfächer belegen, da ich sie vorher nicht belegt habe."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:72
translate german jamie1_e89ebb70:

    # gnd "Oh cool. Quantum Science, like your dad huh?"
    gnd "Oh, cool. Quantenwissenschaft, genau wie dein Vater, was?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:73
translate german jamie1_73fe1c32:

    # pc "Yeah. Different types, but similar."
    pc "Ja. Andere Fachrichtungen, aber ähnlich."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:74
translate german jamie1_d6a36df7:

    # gnd "I wouldn't have expected that from you."
    gnd "Das hätte ich von dir nicht erwartet."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:75
translate german jamie1_d98cce84:

    # pc "Why's that?"
    pc "Warum denn?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:76
translate german jamie1_6e902e84:

    # gnd "Well, you never seemed like the type to enjoy the science and math stuff. I always thought that you'd end up being a used car salesman or something."
    gnd "Na ja, du hast nie den Eindruck gemacht, als würdest du Spaß an Naturwissenschaften und Mathe haben. Ich dachte immer, du würdest am Ende Gebrauchtwagenverkäufer oder so was werden."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:77
translate german jamie1_c0131acd:

    # pc "Wow! Harsh!"
    pc "Wow! Hart!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:80
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/jamie_009.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_009.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:81
translate german jamie1_775544cc:

    # gnd "I'm sorry! I didn't mean anything bad by it, I just meant that you were always very charismatic and fast-talking, but never interested in studies."
    gnd "Tut mir leid! Ich wollte nichts Böses damit sagen, ich meinte nur, dass du immer sehr charismatisch und redegewandt warst, dich aber nie für das Lernen interessiert hast."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:82
translate german jamie1_3b20ba0b:

    # gnd "I should have said lawyer - that would have been nicer, I guess. Not that there's anything wrong with used car salesmen though."
    gnd "Ich hätte Anwalt sagen sollen – das wäre netter gewesen, schätze ich. Nicht, dass an Gebrauchtwagenhändlern irgendwas auszusetzen wäre."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:83
translate german jamie1_d28b9880:

    # pc "Well I'm a lot different than I was when I was 13."
    pc "Nun, ich bin ganz anders als damals, als ich 13 war."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:86
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice "voices/jamie_054.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_054.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:87
translate german jamie1_59601283:

    # gnd "Speaking of when we were 13, there was something I wanted to ask you."
    gnd "Apropos, als wir 13 waren: Da gibt es etwas, das ich dich fragen wollte."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:88
translate german jamie1_88fa21e7:

    # pc "Ask away."
    pc "Frag ruhig."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:90
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice "voices/jamie_055.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_055.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:92
translate german jamie1_7520d05b:

    # gnd "Why did you break up with me?"
    gnd "Warum hast du mit mir Schluss gemacht?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:93
translate german jamie1_7eba9d8e:

    # "My stomach does a sort of backflip. This is not what I had been expecting at all."
    "Mein Magen macht eine Art Salto. Das habe ich überhaupt nicht erwartet."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:94
translate german jamie1_b464fd63:

    # pc "Break up with you? What do you mean?"
    pc "Mit dir Schluss machen? Was meinst du damit?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:97
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice "voices/jamie_056.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_056.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:98
translate german jamie1_208f93af:

    # gnd "In middle school. We had been neighbors and friends for pretty much our whole lives."
    gnd "In der Mittelstufe. Wir waren so ziemlich unser ganzes Leben lang Nachbarn und Freunde gewesen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:100
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_6:

    # voice "voices/jamie_057.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_057.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:101
translate german jamie1_03b1922c:

    # gnd "We'd play at each other's houses. You were my first kiss. You were the first boy to touch my boobs, although there wasn't much there at the time."
    gnd "Wir haben bei einander zu Hause gespielt. Du warst mein erster Kuss. Du warst der erste Junge, der meine Brüste berührt hat, obwohl da damals noch nicht viel war."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:104
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_7:

    # voice "voices/jamie_058.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_058.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:105
translate german jamie1_d37ad228:

    # gnd "We went to Homecoming together. Remember?"
    gnd "Wir sind zusammen zum Homecoming gegangen. Erinnerst du dich?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:108
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_8:

    # voice "voices/jamie_059.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_059.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:109
translate german jamie1_a5fe0c77:

    # gnd "Then, out of nowhere, you just stopped talking to me."
    gnd "Dann hast du aus heiterem Himmel einfach aufgehört, mit mir zu reden."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:111
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_060.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_060.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:112
translate german jamie1_a94569ad:

    # gnd "You didn't come over and see me anymore, you didn't answer my phone calls, you didn't even acknowledge me in the halls at school."
    gnd "Du bist nicht mehr zu mir gekommen, hast meine Anrufe nicht mehr beantwortet, hast mich in den Schulfluren nicht einmal mehr beachtet."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:113
translate german jamie1_60a987f0:

    # pc "Wait, what? I don't remember doing any of that."
    pc "Moment mal, was? Ich kann mich an nichts davon erinnern."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:114
translate german jamie1_7d86fb5a:

    # pc "We just stopped hanging out together. You had different friends and so did I."
    pc "Wir haben einfach aufgehört, zusammen abzuhängen. Du hattest andere Freunde und ich auch."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:116
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_10:

    # voice "voices/jamie_061.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_061.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:117
translate german jamie1_dc86cca2:

    # gnd "Is that what you think happened?"
    gnd "Glaubst du, dass es so war?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:118
translate german jamie1_69b6e4a8:

    # pc "From what I remember. That was a long time ago."
    pc "Soweit ich mich erinnere. Das ist schon lange her."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:120
translate german jamie1_58fea4ec:

    # "She sighs and looks away from me, her bottom lip sticking out. My response obviously made her upset, but I truly don't remember things happening that way."
    "Sie seufzt und wendet ihren Blick von mir ab, die Unterlippe vorstreckend. Meine Antwort hat sie offensichtlich verärgert, aber ich erinnere mich wirklich nicht daran, dass es so abgelaufen ist."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:121
translate german jamie1_a62cc161:

    # "I did stop going over to her house, but that was just because we stopped hanging out as much."
    "Ich habe zwar aufgehört, zu ihr nach Hause zu gehen, aber das lag nur daran, dass wir uns nicht mehr so oft getroffen haben."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:122
translate german jamie1_3ad28c2d:

    # "I might have ignored some of her phone calls, but I don't think it was intentional. I was just doing other things and it slipped my mind."
    "Vielleicht habe ich einige ihrer Anrufe ignoriert, aber ich glaube nicht, dass das absichtlich war. Ich war einfach mit anderen Dingen beschäftigt und habe es vergessen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:123
translate german jamie1_7e6fa894:

    # "And I didn't greet everybody I knew in the halls every time we passed - that's just silly."
    "Und ich habe nicht jedes Mal alle Bekannten im Flur begrüßt, wenn wir aneinander vorbeigegangen sind – das ist doch albern."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:124
translate german jamie1_515956f7:

    # "But there is something else. I do remember being upset at her about something. Maybe I did consciously ignore her?"
    "Aber da ist noch etwas anderes. Ich erinnere mich tatsächlich daran, dass ich wegen irgendetwas sauer auf sie war. Vielleicht habe ich sie doch bewusst ignoriert?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:127
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_11:

    # voice "voices/jamie_062.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_062.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:128
translate german jamie1_dce96005:

    # gnd "It wasn't just the normal growing apart. Something happened, and you just cut me off completely."
    gnd "Es war nicht nur das normale Auseinanderleben. Es ist etwas passiert, und du hast mich einfach komplett aus deinem Leben gestrichen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:130
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_12:

    # voice "voices/jamie_063.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_063.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:131
translate german jamie1_98593801:

    # gnd "Every time I tried to ask you why, you blew me off, until eventually I just got the hint that you didn't like me anymore."
    gnd "Jedes Mal, wenn ich dich fragte, warum, hast du mich abgewimmelt, bis ich schließlich den Hinweis bekam, dass du mich nicht mehr mochtest."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:132
translate german jamie1_306adf54:

    # pc "I didn't stop liking--"
    pc "Ich habe nicht aufgehört, dich zu mögen –"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:134
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_13:

    # voice "voices/jamie_064.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_064.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:135
translate german jamie1_02d938ef:

    # gnd "It was right after that Homecoming dance. We had a good time there. I know we did."
    gnd "Es war direkt nach dem Homecoming-Ball. Wir hatten dort eine schöne Zeit. Ich weiß, dass es so war."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:137
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_14:

    # voice "voices/jamie_065.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_065.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:138
translate german jamie1_b0be8140:

    # gnd "We danced like middle school kids, just holding each other and swaying back and forth."
    gnd "Wir tanzten wie Mittelschüler, hielten uns einfach fest und wiegten uns hin und her."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:140
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_15:

    # voice "voices/jamie_066.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_066.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:141
translate german jamie1_7107383b:

    # gnd "Then we snuck off to the corner and made out for the rest of the night."
    gnd "Dann schlichen wir uns in eine Ecke und knutschten den Rest des Abends."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:143
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_16:

    # voice "voices/jamie_067.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_067.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:144
translate german jamie1_6e0d44b1:

    # gnd "Afterwards, I thought I did something wrong. That you didn't like kissing me or something. That I had made you mad."
    gnd "Danach dachte ich, ich hätte etwas falsch gemacht. Dass du es nicht mochtest, mich zu küssen, oder so. Dass ich dich wütend gemacht hatte."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:146
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_17:

    # voice "voices/jamie_068.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_068.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:147
translate german jamie1_ae5a2abe:

    # gnd "So what was it? What happened?"
    gnd "Also, was war es? Was ist passiert?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:148
translate german jamie1_820e82ce:

    # pc "Homecoming? That was 8th grade?"
    pc "Homecoming? Das war in der 8. Klasse?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:149
translate german jamie1_5c9ff614:

    # "She nods."
    "Sie nickt."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:150
translate german jamie1_dab6ae1d:

    # pc "Ugh. I remember now."
    pc "Ugh. Jetzt erinnere ich mich."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:152
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_18:

    # voice "voices/jamie_069.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_069.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:153
translate german jamie1_27030523:

    # gnd "Oh really?"
    gnd "Ach wirklich?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:154
translate german jamie1_791da015:

    # pc "Do you remember my friend Tosh?"
    pc "Erinnerst du dich an meinen Freund Tosh?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:156
translate german jamie1_3b8202ee:

    # "She nods again."
    "Sie nickt wieder."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:157
translate german jamie1_35a1b275:

    # pc "Well we were best friends at the time. We rode bikes everywhere and played video games together."
    pc "Nun, wir waren damals beste Freunde. Wir sind überall mit dem Fahrrad hingefahren und haben zusammen Videospiele gespielt."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:159
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_19:

    # voice "voices/jamie_070.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_070.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:160
translate german jamie1_5dcba36c:

    # gnd "I remember. You kind of stopped hanging out with me as much once he started coming around."
    gnd "Ich erinnere mich. Du hast irgendwie aufgehört, so oft mit mir abzuhängen, als er anfing, bei uns vorbeizukommen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:161
translate german jamie1_d2697e62:

    # pc "Yeah, well after the Homecoming dance, he told me that he heard you saying stuff in the Spanish class that you shared with him."
    pc "Ja, also, nach dem Homecoming-Ball hat er mir erzählt, dass er gehört hat, wie du in dem Spanischkurs, den ihr gemeinsam hattet, Sachen gesagt hast."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:162
translate german jamie1_09200a36:

    # pc "Stuff like that you didn't really like me and that you only went to the dance with me because I gave you chocolates and flowers and stuff."
    pc "Sachen wie, dass du mich nicht wirklich mochtest und dass du nur mit mir zum Ball gegangen bist, weil ich dir Schokolade und Blumen und so geschenkt habe."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:165
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_20:

    # voice "voices/jamie_071.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_071.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:166
translate german jamie1_9a75f2cb:

    # gnd "That's ridiculous! I never said anything like that!"
    gnd "Das ist lächerlich! So etwas habe ich nie gesagt!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:167
translate german jamie1_358eaba7:

    # pc "I believe you!"
    pc "Ich glaube dir!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:168
translate german jamie1_9638be50:

    # pc "But at the time, I thought that Tosh was completely honest, and I trusted everything he said."
    pc "Aber damals dachte ich, dass Tosh absolut ehrlich war, und ich habe alles geglaubt, was er gesagt hat."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:169
translate german jamie1_89d02a73:

    # pc "It wasn't until high school that I realized that he was completely full of shit."
    pc "Erst in der Highschool wurde mir klar, dass er nur Unsinn geredet hat."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:170
translate german jamie1_b50f91a5:

    # pc "I think he's in jail now."
    pc "Ich glaube, er sitzt jetzt im Gefängnis."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:173
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_21:

    # voice "voices/jamie_072.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_072.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:174
translate german jamie1_11f27db5:

    # gnd "So that's it? We were friends our whole lives, but you trusted some new guy friend from school and didn't even talk to me about it? Didn't even let me defend myself?"
    gnd "Das war’s also? Wir waren unser ganzes Leben lang Freunde, aber du hast einem neuen Kumpel aus der Schule geglaubt und nicht mal mit mir darüber gesprochen? Hast mich nicht mal zu Wort kommen lassen?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:178
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_22:

    # voice "voices/jamie_073.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_073.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:179
translate german jamie1_4975276b:

    # gnd "Hell yes, you were."
    gnd "Und ob du das warst."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:182
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_23:

    # voice "voices/jamie_074.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_074.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:183
translate german jamie1_4e3ae829:

    # gnd "What does it matter?"
    gnd "Was spielt das für eine Rolle?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:185
translate german jamie1_9872e61d:

    # "She looks at me, tears pooling in her eyes."
    "Sie sieht mich an, Tränen steigen ihr in die Augen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:187
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_24:

    # voice "voices/jamie_075.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_075.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:188
translate german jamie1_1692a6fc:

    # gnd "You broke my heart. I know it's all middle school stuff, but you'd be surprised how much things that happen during that time in your life affect your mindset."
    gnd "Du hast mir das Herz gebrochen. Ich weiß, das ist alles nur Mittelstufenkram, aber du würdest dich wundern, wie sehr Dinge, die in dieser Zeit deines Lebens passieren, deine Denkweise beeinflussen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:190
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_25:

    # voice "voices/jamie_076.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_076.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:191
translate german jamie1_76ad11a6:

    # gnd "I was so in love with you, you wouldn't believe it."
    gnd "Ich war so in dich verliebt, du würdest es nicht glauben."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:193
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_26:

    # voice "voices/jamie_077.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_077.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:194
translate german jamie1_e649708c:

    # gnd "You cutting me off like that sort of flipped a switch in my brain."
    gnd "Dass du mich einfach so abgewiesen hast, hat bei mir irgendwie einen Schalter umgelegt."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:196
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_27:

    # voice "voices/jamie_078.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_078.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:197
translate german jamie1_42cafbea:

    # gnd "I shut down for a long time. I didn't trust people, didn't make friends easily."
    gnd "Ich habe mich lange Zeit verschlossen. Ich habe Menschen nicht vertraut, habe nicht leicht Freunde gefunden."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:199
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_28:

    # voice "voices/jamie_079.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_079.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:200
translate german jamie1_58eb925b:

    # gnd "I mostly just laid in my room and studied and cried."
    gnd "Meistens lag ich einfach in meinem Zimmer, habe gelernt und geweint."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:202
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_29:

    # voice "voices/jamie_080.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_080.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:203
translate german jamie1_f2e0045e:

    # gnd "That's why my dad hates you. He saw what you did to me and he's never forgiven you for it."
    gnd "Deshalb hasst dich mein Vater. Er hat gesehen, was du mir angetan hast, und er hat dir das nie verziehen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:206
translate german jamie1_10be1c3b:

    # pc "I'm so sorry. I was a stupid kid, but that's no excuse."
    pc "Es tut mir so leid. Ich war ein dummes Kind, aber das ist keine Entschuldigung."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:207
translate german jamie1_bcb802d4:

    # pc "I should have never treated you like that."
    pc "Ich hätte dich niemals so behandeln dürfen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:209
translate german jamie1_76abefbc:

    # pc "I'm not going to apologize for stuff I did when I was 13 years old. I was a stupid kid. All kids are stupid kids."
    pc "Ich werde mich nicht für Dinge entschuldigen, die ich mit 13 Jahren getan habe. Ich war ein dummes Kind. Alle Kinder sind dumme Kinder."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:212
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_30:

    # voice "voices/jamie_081.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_081.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:213
translate german jamie1_326ba1f0:

    # gnd "You're STILL a stupid kid! I'm done here! This was a mistake! We're not friends, don't talk to me anymore!"
    gnd "Du bist IMMER NOCH ein dummes Kind! Ich bin fertig hier! Das war ein Fehler! Wir sind keine Freunde, sprich nicht mehr mit mir!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:214
translate german jamie1_6ca9d573:

    # "With that, she stands up and walks out of the café."
    "Damit steht sie auf und verlässt das Café."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:215
translate german jamie1_01c3f816:

    # "Others avert their gaze from me, trying to pretend that they hadn't heard what just happened."
    "Die anderen wenden ihren Blick von mir ab und tun so, als hätten sie nicht gehört, was gerade passiert ist."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:216
translate german jamie1_f5d0b218:

    # "This had not gone anything like what I had wanted. I'm not sure if my relationship with Jamie is even salvageable now."
    "Das ist überhaupt nicht so gelaufen, wie ich es mir gewünscht hatte. Ich bin mir nicht sicher, ob meine Beziehung zu Jamie jetzt überhaupt noch zu retten ist."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:217
translate german jamie1_a686ffdc:

    # "I finish up my coffee, thinking about the mistakes I'd made, then I head back out to the car and go to school."
    "Ich trinke meinen Kaffee aus, denke über die Fehler nach, die ich gemacht habe, dann gehe ich zurück zum Auto und fahre zur Schule."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:223
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_31:

    # voice "voices/jamie_082.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_082.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:224
translate german jamie1_4d43b439:

    # gnd "You have no idea how long I've dreamed about hearing you say that."
    gnd "Du hast keine Ahnung, wie lange ich davon geträumt habe, dass du das sagst."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:226
translate german jamie1_b94d1a33:

    # "She takes a deep breath, then reaches across the table and puts her hands on top of mine."
    "Sie atmet tief durch, streckt dann die Hand über den Tisch aus und legt ihre Hände auf meine."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:229
translate german jamie1_d41d8cd9_32:

    # voice "voices/jamie_083.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_083.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:230
translate german jamie1_fa010ee6:

    # gnd "I forgive you."
    gnd "Ich vergebe dir."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:231
translate german jamie1_521ec7fb:

    # pc "Thank you. I want to be friends again. Can we start over?"
    pc "Danke. Ich möchte, dass wir wieder Freunde sind. Können wir von vorne anfangen?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:233
translate german jamie1_07ca4578:

    # gnd "I don't think there's such a thing as starting over, but we can start working on repairing the damage."
    gnd "Ich glaube nicht, dass es so etwas wie einen Neuanfang gibt, aber wir können daran arbeiten, den Schaden wieder gutzumachen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:235
translate german jamie1_88df1b89:

    # gnd "This helped a lot."
    gnd "Das hat mir sehr geholfen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:236
translate german jamie1_ab6c009b:

    # pc "I'm glad. We should do it again."
    pc "Das freut mich. Wir sollten das wiederholen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:237
translate german jamie1_241ea26c:

    # gnd "Definitely. With hopefully less crying."
    gnd "Auf jeden Fall. Hoffentlich mit weniger Tränen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:238
translate german jamie1_c8d9b24c:

    # "We finish up our coffees and walk out to the cars together."
    "Wir trinken unseren Kaffee aus und gehen gemeinsam zu den Autos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:241
translate german jamie1_1b15168b:

    # gnd "Text me sometime, we can go get coffee again or something."
    gnd "Schreib mir mal eine SMS, wir können wieder einen Kaffee trinken gehen oder so."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:242
translate german jamie1_9b5f710f:

    # pc "I will, I promise."
    pc "Das werde ich, versprochen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:244
translate german jamie1_d311130c:

    # gnd "Thanks for this."
    gnd "Danke dafür."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:245
translate german jamie1_ca03cbd8:

    # pc "No, I should be thanking you for giving me another chance."
    pc "Nein, ich sollte dir danken, dass du mir noch eine Chance gibst."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:246
translate german jamie1_861e750f:

    # pc "I'm not going to hurt you again, I promise. I'm not the same person I was then."
    pc "Ich werde dir nicht wieder wehtun, das verspreche ich. Ich bin nicht mehr derselbe Mensch wie damals."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:247
translate german jamie1_18b10010:

    # gnd "I know. I can tell."
    gnd "Ich weiß. Das merke ich."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:249
translate german jamie1_1c4e0503:

    # gnd "I'll see you later."
    gnd "Bis später."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:250
translate german jamie1_d22c868b:

    # "She gets into her car and drives away, back towards her house."
    "Sie steigt in ihr Auto und fährt los, zurück in Richtung ihres Hauses."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:252
translate german jamie1_3aaaf55b:

    # "The coffee date hadn't gone anything like I expected it too, but I am still happy with the outcome."
    "Das Kaffeetrinken war ganz anders verlaufen, als ich es erwartet hatte, aber ich bin trotzdem zufrieden mit dem Ergebnis."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:253
translate german jamie1_d14d202f:

    # "Now that everything is out in the open, It feels like I have a real connection with Jamie."
    "Jetzt, wo alles offen auf dem Tisch liegt, habe ich das Gefühl, eine echte Verbindung zu Jamie zu haben."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:254
translate german jamie1_1cc92515:

    # "I want to treat her right and earn her forgiveness."
    "Ich möchte sie gut behandeln und mir ihre Vergebung verdienen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:255
translate german jamie1_26a71157:

    # "If anything else comes after that, great, but I don't expect it. Not after the way I had treated her."
    "Wenn danach noch etwas kommt, toll, aber ich rechne nicht damit. Nicht nach der Art, wie ich sie behandelt habe."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie1.rpy:256
translate german jamie1_86fdd457:

    # "I get into the car and drive away."
    "Ich steige ins Auto und fahre los."

